<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>The Order of Truth guild</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Lean of povar server">Lean of povar server</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 11:21 p.m. 14/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> The Order of Truth guild<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>The Order of Truth Guild

<P>The Order of truth believes in order, discipline, and the pursuit of truth. The Order will not recruit ogres or trolls for theses races have no order and are filthy animals. The order respects the Gnomes and Halflings and will recruit them. However a Gnome or Halfling will never rise in rank in the order because the order believes that one of such short stature is not fit to order troops with the exception of short stature ones who go above and beyond the call of duty. Dwarves may become officers a bit easier then the Gnomes and Haflings because the order has noticed that all though dwarves are small, they pack a mean punch and they have at times shown the skills needed to command troops. The Order will recruit all classes and all other races then the ones stated above. The Order believes in the pursuit of truth and in that members of the order will journey to the end of Norrath to find out about Norraths history and no foe or friend will hold this Order back from finding the truth.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
